				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$[10\bar 1]$$\end{document} direction of PEA-based RP type and PPD-based DJ type layered perovskites are also ~6.3 Å. This agreement in crystal orientation further suggests the universality of this templated growth mechanism.
